---
import MainLayout from '~/layouts/MainLayout.astro'
---

<MainLayout title="News and Blogs">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-secondary-500 text-white">
    <article class="px-4 py-8 md:py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-screen-lg">
        <div class="aspect-h-9 aspect-w-16">
          <div class="bg-secondary-200"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-md">
        <div class="mb-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-primary-200">
          News &amp; Article / Tips for Travelers
        </div>

        <h2 class="mb-4 font-serif text-4xl lg:mb-6 lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">
          Top 5 Things to Do in Ocho Rios, Jamaica
        </h2>

        <p class="mb-4 text-white/75">
          Ah, Ocho Rios! This charming Caribbean town in Jamaica is a famous tourist destination for
          a handful of good reasons. Situated on the island's north coast, Ocho Rios (translated as
          Eight Rivers) is known for its lovely waterfalls, natural pools and rivers, and thrilling
          adventures.
        </p>

        <div class="text-primary-200">
          <a class="inline-flex items-center" href="">
            <span class="uppercase tracking-wider">Learn more</span>
            <svg
              class="ml-2 h-4 w-4"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="px-4 py-8 md:py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-screen-lg">
        <div class="aspect-h-9 aspect-w-16">
          <div class="bg-secondary-200"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-md">
        <div class="mb-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-primary-200">
          News &amp; Article / Tips for Travelers
        </div>

        <h2 class="mb-4 font-serif text-4xl lg:mb-6 lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">
          What must happen to plan a successful event?
        </h2>

        <p class="mb-4 text-white/75">
          Planning a successful event takes a lot of work! From business meetings and corporate
          get-togethers to charity events and family reunions, organizing an event that everyone
          will love requires attention to detail and lots of hard prep.
        </p>

        <div class="text-primary-200">
          <a class="inline-flex items-center" href="">
            <span class="uppercase tracking-wider">Learn more</span>
            <svg
              class="ml-2 h-4 w-4"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
